==English==
[[Image:Dangclass8.png|thumb|Corrosive warning symbol]]
===Adjective===
'''corrosive''' (''no [[comparative]] or [[superlative]]'')
# Eating away; having the power of gradually wearing, hanging, or destroying the texture or substance of a body; as, the corrosive action of an acid.
# Having the quality of fretting or vexing.

===Adverb===
'''corrosively'''
# In a corrosive manner.

===Noun===
'''corrosive'''
# That which has the quality of eating or wearing away gradually.
# Any solid, liquid, or gas capable of irreparably harming living tissues or damaging material on contact.
'''corrosiveness'''

